 {"id":"bd-sy6p","title":"[AA][DPOR] DPOR implementation + independence relation","description":"## Goal
Implement DPOR (partial order reduction) using the trace‑monoid model.

## Why
Exploring all interleavings is infeasible; DPOR reduces exploration while preserving coverage.

## Deliverables
- DPOR algorithm integrated with scheduler.
- Independence relation definition for events.
- Metrics: coverage vs. explored schedules.

